column1: UNWIND range(1,1000) as i WITH i CREATE (p:Product {id:i}) WITH i, p UNWIND range(1,5) as j CREATE (e:Element {name:toString(i)+'-'+toString(j)}) CREATE (p)-[:HAS_ELEMENT]->(e)
CREATE TEXT INDEX location_name FOR (n:Location) ON (n.name)
CREATE FULLTEXT INDEX FT2 FOR (n:Person) ON EACH [n.surname]
EXPLAIN UNWIND [1,2,3] as x		return x
cypher runtime=slotted UNWIND [1,2,3] as x		return x
UNWIND $_batch AS _batch WITH _batch.x AS x  return x
